WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 29]

01:54.200 --> 01:56.180
To open a spacetime rift spanning fifty years

01:57.200 --> 01:59.130
requires me to disperse all of my cultivation

01:59.840 --> 02:01.570
and transform into a demon form.

02:04.350 --> 02:06.180
And maintaining the rift will inflict

02:06.710 --> 02:07.850
continuous, severe damage

02:08.120 --> 02:09.490
on the spellcaster.

02:10.040 --> 02:11.570
Lu Wuyi went on continuous rewinds

02:11.920 --> 02:13.020
with Lonescale's power.

02:13.560 --> 02:15.340
The Oracle Stone has provided her

02:15.360 --> 02:16.580
with endless power,

02:17.080 --> 02:18.650
but she's still heavily wounded.

02:20.360 --> 02:21.580
So this time,

02:22.400 --> 02:23.620
Li Jie,

02:25.310 --> 02:26.420
you have to do it.

02:28.000 --> 02:28.650
Hua Qi.

02:29.080 --> 02:30.860
You must keep healing him

02:31.310 --> 02:32.810
with the method of purification.

02:33.400 --> 02:34.590
Otherwise, he won't be able

02:34.590 --> 02:36.690
to bear the pain of maintaining the rift.

02:43.560 --> 02:44.460
Mo Yuntan.

02:44.680 --> 02:45.860
Your formation

02:46.060 --> 02:47.860
can withstand spell attacks.

02:48.910 --> 02:50.180
Keep them safe.

02:51.520 --> 02:52.210
Shiguang.

02:52.470 --> 02:53.930
You will deal with Jiu Ying.

02:54.520 --> 02:56.580
You're the last dragon in the world.

02:57.030 --> 02:59.970
I hope you save the world.

03:15.030 --> 03:16.810
Leave the rewind

03:17.960 --> 03:19.060
to me.

03:21.080 --> 03:22.930
Lu Wuyi is my fated one.

03:24.080 --> 03:25.810
If she is doomed to perish,

03:26.840 --> 03:27.970
then I shall be the one

03:29.520 --> 03:31.180
who brings everything to an end.

03:36.840 --> 03:38.930
You must create another exit

03:39.310 --> 03:41.340
with your own strength in the rift.

03:42.960 --> 03:45.020
I'll maintain the exit here

03:45.560 --> 03:47.340
with all my remaining power.

03:47.710 --> 03:49.090
Make it quick.

03:50.470 --> 03:51.930
If you can't return in time,

03:52.800 --> 03:54.690
you'll be trapped in the rift

03:54.870 --> 03:56.340
and taken to the unknown.

03:57.590 --> 03:58.460
You may even

03:59.560 --> 04:00.860
cease to exist.

04:31.120 --> 04:31.780
Come on.

04:32.890 --> 04:35.270
A constant stream of fear and despair.

04:35.740 --> 04:36.740
Wu Shiguang.

04:37.140 --> 04:38.420
How are you going to beat me?

05:22.430 --> 05:23.450
With your twin blades

05:23.800 --> 05:24.980
unsheathed,

05:26.190 --> 05:27.930
this empty chest of yours

05:28.430 --> 05:30.010
is as vulnerable as a sheet of paper.

05:56.160 --> 05:57.620
Hua Qi, don't be distracted.

05:57.800 --> 05:58.810
Keep healing Li Jie.

06:39.870 --> 06:40.540
The earthquake

06:42.190 --> 06:42.930
stopped.

06:45.480 --> 06:46.420
Wu Wangyan

06:47.560 --> 06:48.660
is still so silly.

06:49.830 --> 06:50.740
What did you say?

06:52.270 --> 06:54.420
Why do you think the Four-Pillar Formation stopped?

06:56.530 --> 06:58.690
Because they sacrificed themselves.

07:58.800 --> 07:59.300
Jin Zheng.

08:54.790 --> 08:55.930
My soul I devote.

08:57.390 --> 08:58.590
Long live the dragon.

08:58.590 --> 08:59.420
Mo Yuntan.

08:59.750 --> 09:00.380
No!

09:25.840 --> 09:27.450
You annoying junior.

09:29.510 --> 09:30.850
Hurry up and become a double-flower.

09:32.440 --> 09:33.090
Congratulations

09:33.630 --> 09:34.660
on becoming a double-flower.

09:42.790 --> 09:43.690
Cherish me.

09:44.020 --> 09:44.850
Only I would

09:44.960 --> 09:45.900
call you Senior.

10:10.600 --> 10:12.780
You must create another exit

10:13.200 --> 10:15.180
with your own strength in the rift.

10:16.120 --> 10:17.570
Although you have

10:17.600 --> 10:19.210
the Dragon Deity's Power of Chi Wen,

10:20.000 --> 10:22.380
you can't reach the realm of the six-flower yet.

10:23.600 --> 10:24.660
Just do your best.

11:14.980 --> 11:17.100
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

11:17.180 --> 11:22.300
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

11:22.620 --> 11:24.740
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

11:24.820 --> 11:29.820
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

11:30.300 --> 11:32.340
♪It's your light, your storms♪

11:32.380 --> 11:37.420
♪Your watchful eyes that set the night alight♪

11:37.540 --> 11:40.580
♪And lead me♪

11:40.980 --> 11:47.740
♪Sailing afar♪

12:31.140 --> 12:33.260
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

12:33.340 --> 12:38.460
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

12:38.780 --> 12:40.980
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

12:41.100 --> 12:45.900
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear...♪

12:47.870 --> 12:49.730
Wrathful sandstorm.

12:53.700 --> 12:56.940
♪Stay with me...♪

12:57.720 --> 12:59.260
Eastern Purple Lightning.

12:59.750 --> 13:01.210
Searing flames.

13:02.150 --> 13:03.900
By the fox's call.

13:04.720 --> 13:06.210
Rewind of Sun and Moon.

13:15.030 --> 13:16.690
Grant me your power.

13:20.870 --> 13:21.810
Master Ji Ling.

13:22.750 --> 13:23.730
From now on,

13:24.910 --> 13:26.260
you're on your own.

13:30.910 --> 13:31.930
Part!

14:37.870 --> 14:39.810
How dare you trespass into the Formless Moon?

14:40.750 --> 14:41.810
Who are you?

14:49.440 --> 14:51.330
The man who came to take your life.

16:24.790 --> 16:25.660
Ji Ling.

16:35.200 --> 16:35.970
Where is Ji Ling?

16:37.360 --> 16:38.140
Lu Wuyi.

17:12.110 --> 17:13.170
Use the Guili Sword

17:14.440 --> 17:15.780
and the Dragon Deity's Power

17:17.350 --> 17:18.610
to destroy the last shard

17:18.640 --> 17:19.780
of the Oracle Stone.

17:20.830 --> 17:21.810
Only then

17:24.960 --> 17:27.020
can you kill Jiu Ying for good.

17:28.350 --> 17:30.020
But you'll also die.

17:38.160 --> 17:39.810
I was never supposed to exist.

17:45.550 --> 17:46.300
Wu Shiguang.

17:48.750 --> 17:50.130
Tell Wangyan

17:53.750 --> 17:54.940
that I miss her.

18:49.550 --> 18:51.330
No.

18:52.080 --> 18:54.420
You're dying with me.

19:10.000 --> 19:10.650
Ji Ling.

19:40.440 --> 19:41.500
Ji Ling.

19:44.350 --> 19:45.540
I'm coming to you.

19:48.030 --> 19:48.890
Don't cry.

19:50.750 --> 19:51.370
Don't cry.

19:52.790 --> 19:54.130
I'll wait for you over there.

19:55.720 --> 19:58.330
I'll pick you up with a bundle of flowers.

20:00.000 --> 20:01.740
A huge bundle.

20:03.550 --> 20:04.170
This way,

20:06.240 --> 20:07.890
you won't be afraid.

20:10.310 --> 20:12.300
Remember to pick me up with flowers.

20:15.270 --> 20:17.420
I want a huge bundle of flowers.

20:17.420 --> 20:19.580
♪Another year has gone by♪

20:20.140 --> 20:24.100
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

20:24.620 --> 20:28.620
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

20:29.020 --> 20:32.100
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

20:32.740 --> 20:37.380
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

20:37.780 --> 20:41.740
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

20:42.140 --> 20:45.980
♪Your silence turns into my hoarse voice♪

20:46.420 --> 20:49.780
♪You left behind your final words♪

20:50.180 --> 20:56.820
♪And every word became a scar♪

21:12.140 --> 21:14.060
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

21:16.500 --> 21:18.540
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

21:43.070 --> 21:44.220
Who are you?

21:51.030 --> 21:52.220
Where am I?

22:01.920 --> 22:02.780
Are you also

22:04.680 --> 22:05.940
going to kill me?

22:10.350 --> 22:11.610
I've been looking for you.

22:13.440 --> 22:14.650
I'll take you home.

22:21.720 --> 22:22.700
I'm scared.

22:25.200 --> 22:26.090
Of me?

22:33.510 --> 22:34.540
Of this place.

22:35.310 --> 22:36.130
It's so dark

22:37.550 --> 22:38.370
and so cold.

22:41.270 --> 22:42.810
But I don't know why

22:45.830 --> 22:46.940
I feel at ease

22:48.960 --> 22:50.330
looking at you.

23:04.480 --> 23:05.570
Then just look at me.

23:07.000 --> 23:07.650
This way,

23:08.720 --> 23:09.980
you won't be afraid.

23:14.350 --> 23:15.980
I think I'm really not afraid anymore.

23:21.550 --> 23:22.940
What's your name?

23:26.790 --> 23:27.700
My name is

23:31.310 --> 23:32.060
Ji Ling.

23:33.960 --> 23:35.500
"Ji" as in "a temporary lodging."

23:37.110 --> 23:38.460
"Ling" as in "hearts connected."

23:45.110 --> 23:46.890
Ji Ling.

23:51.270 --> 23:52.500
I'll remember it.

24:07.440 --> 24:08.130
Go to sleep.

24:11.620 --> 24:13.660
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

24:22.260 --> 24:24.740
♪Don't be sad♪

24:24.740 --> 24:26.460
♪Through every yesterday♪

24:26.540 --> 24:29.060
♪Don't you cry♪

24:29.060 --> 24:30.940
♪Through every memory♪

24:31.020 --> 24:38.460
♪I'll always stay with you♪

24:40.900 --> 24:43.580
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

24:44.140 --> 24:48.020
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

24:48.420 --> 24:52.060
♪I call for you, my only one♪

24:52.580 --> 24:57.340
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

24:57.350 --> 24:57.940
Li Jie.

25:01.590 --> 25:02.330
Master Dragon Deity.

25:08.720 --> 25:09.540
Master Dragon Deity.

25:11.720 --> 25:12.700
Master Dragon Deity.

25:12.790 --> 25:13.890
We did it.

25:15.030 --> 25:15.980
We did it.

25:17.590 --> 25:18.410
Master Dragon Deity.

25:18.510 --> 25:19.330
We did it.

25:20.480 --> 25:21.090
Thank you.

25:22.880 --> 25:23.700
Thank you all.

25:26.440 --> 25:27.060
Thank you.

25:56.240 --> 25:56.980
Don't be sad.

25:58.350 --> 26:00.500
Maybe they just went to another world.

26:02.880 --> 26:03.650
Or perhaps,

26:04.790 --> 26:07.370
Ji Ling chose to stay in the spacetime rift.

26:08.510 --> 26:10.370
I bet he didn't want to come back

26:12.000 --> 26:14.170
to this world where Lu Wuyi never existed.

26:33.510 --> 26:34.130
Wu Wangyan.

26:35.400 --> 26:35.980
You Chi.

26:37.880 --> 26:38.500
Wu Wangyan.

27:39.310 --> 27:40.850
I always called you a coward

27:42.400 --> 27:43.650
who runs away from danger.

27:44.310 --> 27:45.500
Why didn't you run?

27:52.350 --> 27:53.410
Why didn't you run?

27:54.590 --> 27:55.740
Why didn't you run?

29:08.790 --> 29:09.810
Wu Shiguang.

29:12.240 --> 29:13.170
In this life,

29:15.480 --> 29:16.740
I can't repay

29:20.830 --> 29:21.940
your deep affection.

29:24.640 --> 29:25.940
If there is an afterlife,

29:27.000 --> 29:28.500
I swear I will find you.

29:33.500 --> 29:40.140
♪I walk into the twilight amid the fishermen's songs♪

29:45.510 --> 29:47.020
Please save my sister.

29:47.380 --> 29:50.700
♪Heavy snow embraces the fog♪

29:50.820 --> 29:54.540
♪Fading to white, full of bitterness and joy♪

29:54.780 --> 30:01.580
♪Who is reluctant to leave?♪

30:16.620 --> 30:22.260
♪The one in my dream sits lightly by the water♪

30:22.700 --> 30:28.860
♪Watching the sunset, so dim, so full of sorrow♪

30:30.500 --> 30:36.180
♪Lend me a beam of moonlight to light the long way I've come♪

30:36.420 --> 30:42.580
♪I walked, then stopped, then looked, then longed♪

30:46.980 --> 30:49.860
♪Go to a foreign land♪

30:53.500 --> 30:56.700
♪Start wandering♪

31:00.460 --> 31:04.260
♪Like fleeting shadows, a hundred years slip by♪

31:04.420 --> 31:10.700
♪Let love and hate drift out of sight♪

31:11.060 --> 31:17.540
♪I walk into a heartbreak burning bright♪

31:17.860 --> 31:24.740
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft♪

31:24.820 --> 31:27.940
♪Tears slowly turn to frost♪

31:28.300 --> 31:31.900
♪Fading to white, all is lost♪

31:32.180 --> 31:39.460
♪When I wake, who's by my side?♪

32:22.680 --> 32:23.300
Are you scared?

32:27.970 --> 32:28.880
No.

33:05.020 --> 33:10.660
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high♪

33:11.100 --> 33:17.260
♪Wiping away the dark to let the moonlight shine♪

33:17.700 --> 33:19.100
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

33:19.260 --> 33:20.820
♪Bitter and sweet♪

33:21.020 --> 33:24.180
♪The moon stays by my side♪

33:24.620 --> 33:30.420
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

33:50.920 --> 33:52.170
Morning, Master Dragon Deity.

33:55.270 --> 33:56.090
Master Dragon Deity.

33:59.510 --> 34:00.300
Wu Shiguang.

34:02.400 --> 34:03.460
What are you doing here?

34:55.710 --> 34:56.290
What's wrong?

35:06.230 --> 35:07.540
What happened to your face?

35:09.320 --> 35:10.420
Got into a fight again?

35:15.400 --> 35:16.500
I've been busy these days.

35:18.150 --> 35:19.860
Being a commander of the Shilin Sect

35:20.280 --> 35:21.690
is harder than I thought.

35:22.150 --> 35:22.650
But

35:23.150 --> 35:23.980
Father always said,

35:24.760 --> 35:26.170
"Do your best."

35:30.000 --> 35:30.860
Work harder.

35:35.070 --> 35:36.020
You've always been

35:36.880 --> 35:37.900
such a crybaby.

35:38.550 --> 35:39.980
You're the Master Dragon Deity now.

35:40.440 --> 35:42.460
You can't be that scared little boy anymore.

36:06.480 --> 36:07.060
What's wrong?

36:07.670 --> 36:08.460
Had a nightmare?

36:10.760 --> 36:11.250
No.

36:13.550 --> 36:14.690
It was a sweet dream.

36:21.280 --> 36:22.420
But then I woke up.

36:24.960 --> 36:26.170
So I'm a bit upset.

36:29.440 --> 36:30.690
I came to tell you

36:31.670 --> 36:33.570
that the Oracle Stone gave a new prophecy.

36:36.150 --> 36:37.020
The old dragon falls.

36:37.670 --> 36:38.570
The new dragon rises.

36:39.320 --> 36:40.540
Rewind the river of time.

36:41.480 --> 36:42.650
A new chapter has started.

37:04.630 --> 37:05.980
You've become the Master Dragon Deity.

37:07.150 --> 37:08.290
I have to work harder

37:09.150 --> 37:10.340
to be a great hero

37:10.360 --> 37:11.770
and honor our ancestors.

37:17.960 --> 37:19.500
You're already a great hero.

37:22.590 --> 37:23.290
Again?

37:24.030 --> 37:24.860
Father once said,

37:26.230 --> 37:27.290
"Be down to earth.

37:27.960 --> 37:29.020
Stop daydreaming."

37:30.100 --> 37:35.220
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams♪

37:36.420 --> 37:41.420
♪I stay silent, afraid the fire in my heart will rise...♪

37:43.880 --> 37:44.500
Miss Mu Long.

37:48.280 --> 37:50.020
You came to offer incense too?

37:52.230 --> 37:54.650
[Tales Told by Mu, Mu Long]
I finished my book.

37:55.440 --> 37:57.290
Want to read it?

37:58.550 --> 37:59.570
O-Of course.

38:00.030 --> 38:01.060
I want to be your first...

38:03.920 --> 38:04.770
first reader.

38:08.260 --> 38:10.060
[Tales Told by Mu, Mu Long]

38:10.460 --> 38:13.620
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

38:13.780 --> 38:17.100
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness♪

38:17.300 --> 38:20.140
♪Watching the corner of your lips stained♪

38:20.220 --> 38:22.940
♪With a touch of dark crimson...♪

38:29.760 --> 38:30.290
Brother.

38:30.320 --> 38:31.380
Do you have any coins?

38:31.590 --> 38:33.170
Can I get a coin

38:33.230 --> 38:35.090
for the Pond of Merit to make a wish?

38:37.860 --> 38:40.980
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you♪

38:43.150 --> 38:44.010
Master Dragon Deity

38:44.010 --> 38:45.420
will keep blessing us.

38:46.630 --> 38:48.320
Look, a double-flower hunter.

38:48.440 --> 38:49.940
I saw a double-flower hunter.

38:50.110 --> 38:51.820
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

38:56.840 --> 38:58.340
I saw a double-flower hunter.

38:59.070 --> 39:00.900
The middle one has one more flower.

39:01.110 --> 39:02.020
Triple-flower.

39:02.400 --> 39:03.290
Triple-flower.

39:03.840 --> 39:04.900
Come and see!

39:05.590 --> 39:06.940
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:07.000 --> 39:08.690
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:08.760 --> 39:10.460
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:10.480 --> 39:12.060
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:12.070 --> 39:13.940
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:22.710 --> 39:23.290
Ji Ling.

39:24.510 --> 39:25.500
Do you see it?

39:26.630 --> 39:27.710
It's the wonderful world

39:27.710 --> 39:29.060
you died to protect.

39:31.550 --> 39:32.980
I'll keep guarding it.

39:34.630 --> 39:36.130
As long as there are dragons,

39:37.150 --> 39:39.940
the light of faith will not be extinguished.

39:39.940 --> 39:44.580
♪Watch the spring breeze stir the warm sun, flowers across the hills♪

39:44.940 --> 39:50.740
♪Summer days run long, and flowing rain carries me afar...♪

39:54.280 --> 39:55.020
Wu Wangyan.

39:57.660 --> 40:02.620
♪A face worn old by wind, snow, and frost♪

40:03.740 --> 40:10.060
♪But my tears still burn hot♪

40:14.030 --> 40:14.820
You are...

40:16.380 --> 40:22.420
♪Hair turns white in time's flow♪

40:22.620 --> 40:26.700
♪My time with you♪

40:29.140 --> 40:33.900
♪Moon, oh moon, why veil your light in frost?♪

40:34.340 --> 40:39.940
♪In my dreams, she leans by the window, lost...♪

40:43.030 --> 40:45.060
Why do you have my hair?

40:46.940 --> 40:52.460
♪From afar, is it you singing soft and low?♪

40:53.590 --> 40:54.420
That is

40:57.000 --> 40:57.690
a long story

40:59.030 --> 41:00.250
to be told.

41:02.580 --> 41:05.220
♪Ripples dance in silver glow♪

41:05.220 --> 41:08.580
♪A harbor warm from yesterday♪

41:08.700 --> 41:11.540
♪Hair turns white in time's flow♪

41:11.780 --> 41:14.580
♪You rest upon my shoulder♪

41:14.780 --> 41:18.860
♪Take me back where we belong♪

41:26.400 --> 41:27.130
Once,

41:27.630 --> 41:30.020
I thought the mission was everything,

41:30.840 --> 41:33.980
but never thought that the mission would come to an end.

41:35.230 --> 41:37.250
Maybe it's time to let go

41:37.760 --> 41:40.170
and see the world out there.

41:41.880 --> 41:44.500
Maybe I'll figure out who I am

41:45.280 --> 41:47.170
and the meaning of my existence.

41:48.070 --> 41:50.340
And this is probably the answer

41:51.190 --> 41:52.570
all of us

41:53.280 --> 41:54.980
are seeking our entire lives.

41:56.920 --> 41:57.740
Come and find me.

42:00.960 --> 42:01.730
And

42:01.880 --> 42:04.250
I think there is a voice

42:04.360 --> 42:06.290
telling me to find someone.

42:06.290 --> 42:08.340
But I don't know where to find that person.

42:08.610 --> 42:11.090
I don't even know his name.

42:15.660 --> 42:18.860
[Moonlight over the wasteland. Scales bless all creatures.]

42:18.860 --> 42:22.060
[Gorgeous as a dream. Fate's paths converge.]

42:22.060 --> 42:27.940
[Veil of Shadows]

42:31.030 --> 42:33.500
Demons coming!

42:33.630 --> 42:36.020
Demons coming!

42:36.280 --> 42:38.020
- Here to catch you. - Be careful.

42:38.190 --> 42:39.020
Come here.

42:40.510 --> 42:41.460
There are no demons

42:41.630 --> 42:42.460
in the world.

42:42.960 --> 42:44.900
Those are stories adults made up

42:44.920 --> 42:46.190
to scare the kids.

42:46.670 --> 42:48.500
How boring.

42:49.000 --> 42:50.860
It would be so much fun

42:51.030 --> 42:52.130
if there were demons.

42:53.620 --> 42:54.080
Here.

42:54.960 --> 42:57.440
Demons coming!

42:57.510 --> 42:59.190
Demons coming to catch you!

42:59.190 --> 43:01.050
Demons coming to catch you!

43:01.230 --> 43:02.340
Demons coming!

43:02.800 --> 43:04.020
Here to catch you!

43:36.740 --> 43:40.180
♪If there's a little village down the road♪

43:40.900 --> 43:43.140
♪By a river bending soft and slow♪

43:43.540 --> 43:48.500
♪You hum a tune by the fire's glow♪

43:49.380 --> 43:52.740
♪Time would linger, never go♪

43:53.140 --> 43:57.740
♪Even the wind would fade, just you and me♪

43:58.260 --> 44:01.500
♪Hand in hand, we'd sit close, quietly♪

44:07.280 --> 44:08.540
Young Miss, do you like flowers?

44:13.760 --> 44:14.460
Yes, I do.

44:15.550 --> 44:16.460
Would you like some?

44:19.710 --> 44:20.650
All fresh.

44:20.800 --> 44:21.500
I just picked them.

44:23.800 --> 44:24.290
I...

44:26.360 --> 44:27.290
have no money.

44:32.630 --> 44:34.060
I'm just a worker here.

44:34.920 --> 44:36.290
If I were the boss,

44:37.400 --> 44:38.540
I would give you some.

44:39.480 --> 44:40.460
What should I do?

44:41.800 --> 44:42.940
No need.

44:43.480 --> 44:44.650
You don't have to do this.

44:45.400 --> 44:45.940
Thank you.

44:48.700 --> 44:55.100
♪Shadows rush like waves in my mind♪

44:55.580 --> 44:57.340
♪Watch the moon rise, wait for daylight to go♪

44:57.500 --> 45:01.300
♪Back to back, we lost ourselves in time we let go...♪

45:04.630 --> 45:05.170
Young Miss.

45:08.500 --> 45:10.060
♪I know you're waiting for me♪

45:10.180 --> 45:13.660
♪With flowers in hand, I'm on my way to you♪

45:14.540 --> 45:20.940
♪You're the brightest moon I know♪

45:21.300 --> 45:26.860
♪Sweetest berry that ever grew...♪

45:27.000 --> 45:27.460
Here.

45:27.460 --> 45:33.660
♪I was a drifter on the road♪

45:34.100 --> 45:39.820
♪Till you gave me a story to hold...♪

45:41.870 --> 45:42.260
You...

45:42.440 --> 45:43.360
You don't want them?

45:44.550 --> 45:46.900
I picked these raspberries by the lake near home.

45:47.280 --> 45:47.930
Do...

45:48.280 --> 45:49.890
Do you like raspberries?

46:05.780 --> 46:09.380
♪They say if we loved once before♪

46:09.940 --> 46:12.140
♪Even apart, we still feel it all♪

46:12.540 --> 46:17.540
♪Like thousands of blooms on that shore...♪

46:19.800 --> 46:20.630
So sweet.

46:22.180 --> 46:26.820
♪You smile at me, but it's bittersweet♪

46:27.300 --> 46:30.540
♪Still, not a word I hear♪

46:31.340 --> 46:37.820
♪The river of time flows under the bridge♪

46:38.140 --> 46:43.820
♪Hugging each other, we slowly grow old♪

46:44.180 --> 46:50.580
♪Don't be afraid to be forgotten by the world♪

46:50.940 --> 46:56.740
♪I'll tell you the story from the beginning♪

46:56.740 --> 47:04.280
[No matter how the universe changes,]

47:04.280 --> 47:11.820
[I will always be by your side.]

47:11.820 --> 47:16.580
[Veil of Shadows]

47:17.860 --> 47:22.060
♪We take life and death in stride, with no fear and no sorrow♪

47:22.500 --> 47:26.580
♪We raise our bowls to the sky, hot blood burning, cold tears gleaming♪

47:27.060 --> 47:28.780
♪Moon and scales shine in radiant splendor♪

47:29.220 --> 47:31.300
♪As the winds rise, dragons and foxes cry in strife♪

47:31.700 --> 47:35.980
♪At the world's end, the destined soul rides proud and free♪

47:36.420 --> 47:38.380
♪I am fearless♪

47:38.820 --> 47:40.780
♪I will gather light to mend the moon for you♪

47:41.180 --> 47:45.580
♪When heaven and earth are reborn, we will meet again♪

